{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/issues/3/comments/40470989.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/issues/3#comment-40470989"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/issues/3.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 3, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}ts=default"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-cmake", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake", "uuid": "{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}"}, "title": "Clarify desired location of copyright notices in cmake modules"}, "content": {"raw": "Regarding the testing, it doesn't look like we're making use of `CTest`, so I'd rather not pull that in entirely, but it does make sense for us to use an option called `BUILD_TESTING` if that's a conventional name for a testing toggle variable.\n\nRegarding the copyright notices, I don't really have an opinion on the matter, so I'd very much welcome feedback on what style we should prefer for cmake modules.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Regarding the testing, it doesn't look like we're making use of <code>CTest</code>, so I'd rather not pull that in entirely, but it does make sense for us to use an option called <code>BUILD_TESTING</code> if that's a conventional name for a testing toggle variable.</p>\n<p>Regarding the copyright notices, I don't really have an opinion on the matter, so I'd very much welcome feedback on what style we should prefer for cmake modules.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-10-11T21:41:05.750782+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 40470989}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/issues/3/comments/41037911.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/issues/3#comment-41037911"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/issues/3.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 3, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}ts=default"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-cmake", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake", "uuid": "{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}"}, "title": "Clarify desired location of copyright notices in cmake modules"}, "content": {"raw": "We are now using `BUILD_TESTING` as of pull request #6 and pull request #7.\n\nSo the only unresolved comment is the location of copyright notices for cmake modules. I'll edit the issue title to match.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>We are now using <code>BUILD_TESTING</code> as of <a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/6/proposal-updating-to-visual-studio-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #6</a> and <a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/7/add-an-example-with-externalproject\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #7</a>.</p>\n<p>So the only unresolved comment is the location of copyright notices for cmake modules. I'll edit the issue title to match.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-11-06T18:12:38.245507+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 41037911}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/issues/3/comments/41037919.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/issues/3#comment-41037919"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/issues/3.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 3, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}ts=default"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-cmake", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake", "uuid": "{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}"}, "title": "Clarify desired location of copyright notices in cmake modules"}, "content": {"raw": null, "markup": "markdown", "html": "", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-11-06T18:13:09.702040+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.